item.title: Rehearsal Schedule
item.description: Our rehearsals are likely going to be on Tuesday, Thursdays and Saturdays. We will organize our rehearsals around Heather’s, to allow performers to do both. First rehearsal will be May 26th. Our fist choreo rehearsal will be June 10th. Stay tuned for more!
